subject: Bowl Games
Football (College)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Notre Dame, one year removed from playing for the national championship, struggled past proud Rutgers in the fourth annual Pinstripe Bowl on Saturday at Yankee Stadium.
